headline: YOLO, Fly SOLO: United Airlines Shares How Travelers Can Treat Themselves Ahead of National Plan a Solo Vacation Day
summary: This love-filled February, solo travel is on the rise and United is sharing travel hacks, popular destinations and app features to empower adventurers to get ready for National Plan a Solo Vacation Day on March 1 with the ultimate travel mantra: YOLO (You Only Live Once), Fly SOLO.

headline: Private High-Speed Rail Pioneer iryo Becomes First UATP Rail Merchant in Spain
summary: UATP, the global network that enables organizations to simplify payment processes and expand their payment capabilities, today announced that iryo, the leading Spanish private high-speed railway operator by number of frequencies owned by its partners Trenitalia, Air Nostrum and Globalvia, has become a UATP Merchant. The partnership enables iryo to accept UATP payments for train bookings, a critical capability as demand for rail travel surges.
